How to Compile and Run (Linux)

Step 1: Save both files:

  command: nano SlidSender.java
  command: nano SlidReceiver.java


Step 2: Compile them:

  command: javac SlidSender.java SlidReceiver.java


Step 3: Run them in separate terminals:

Terminal 1 (Sender):

  command: java SlidSender


Terminal 2 (Receiver):

  command: java SlidReceiver
